text: Consuming silver particles kills novel coronavirus
An image shared on Facebook claims colloidal silver can kill the new coronavirus and more than 650 other pathogens.
Vitamin D, vitamin C, colloidal silver and black seed oil can kill the coronavirus.
entity_strings: black seed, colloidal silver, coronavirus, vitamin

text: If the new coronavirus is exposed to a temperature of 26-27oC it will be killed, as it does not live in hot regions. Also drinking hot water and sun exposure will do the trick and staying away from ice cream and cold food is advised.
